The Department of Energy made the new fuel prices available and it is not good news.Petrol will increase with 45c per liter while diesel climbs with another staggering 63c. Illuminating Paraffin will also go up with between 57c and 76c while LP gas is set to jump up 59c per kilogram.Also read: The real price of fuel in South Africa &#8211; where is the rest of our money going?